channel.title: Server Unexpected Respond
channel.description:
Hello, I am back to Runescape stuff now, havent checked this forum for more than years now, i pretty did read all stuff.
i did manged to get working server long time ago.
now only problem i have is, "unexpected server respond, please try different world"
ive try 3 different server files,
2-3 different clients, same prob anyone kno why
if you need some more info about anything lemme know.

item.title: Server Unexpected Respond
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

that normally means you were ip banned… check the ipban list and make sure your not in it XD if your not… then try another… i personaly used reapagesape V2 for my base…its not the best but its great for starters…and it is a 317… making it fairly simple compared to the newer versions
